      "rationale": "All three FEA codes in the ensemble operate under documented software QA plans. Version control and regression test suites are maintained. Ansys is a commercially validated solver; FDA and DePuy Synthes in-house codes are subject to internal configuration management procedures. Gradation 2 achieved and required."
