      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties, geometry, and boundary conditions traceable to measured data or certified material specifications; uncertainty in inputs quantified.",
      "rationale": "Material properties are sourced from ASTM F136 certified material test reports for the specific Ti-6Al-4V ELI lot used in manufacture. Geometry is derived from CMM measurements of production screws. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry. Input uncertainties are propagated through the model using a Monte Carlo approach (n=1000 samples). Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
