      "rationale": "A formal input equivalency table maps each experimental measurement (geometry, material lot, fixture dimensions, applied displacement) to the corresponding FEA model parameter. Discrepancies are quantified as uncertainty contributions and included in the validation uncertainty budget. Gradation 3 achieved."
