      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria: E/uval <1.96 and percent difference <10%. Comparison plots with experimental uncertainty bands and model prediction intervals are documented. Gradation 3 achieved."
