      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in FDA guidance for pedicle screw system submissions under ASTM F1717. Each QoI is directly linked to a device failure mode (fatigue initiation, permanent deformation, structural integrity). Relevance is documented in the V&V plan. Gradation 3 achieved."
